 src="https://i.imgur.com/m0WjLYl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6gjhUNe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jCkII5F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RppEzt0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GEgQmpy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xG4bMdY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZbOAvys.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/acjiZ19</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CloudMage]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shop wisely ...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xj6SNA6</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/It9ZS0r.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xj6SNA6</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[blank666man]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>AOC didn’t deck him, but he definitely deserved it.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yrDBSia</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bPNcNZ3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>________
EDIT:: just got the notification - a little clarity at the onset. I didn’t anticipate this to go off like it did. I made this post to give context in a comment on another post. Someone had said that AOC hit this catcaller, which was untrue. She posted this to her IG story Wednesday evening to talk about how shitty it is that toxic masculinity is so entrenched in our social structure that the Capitol police didn’t even bat an eye when this happened. And then opened the conversation about how we all can talk about these things and stop letting shitty humans be shitty humans. 
________

Posting mostly to reference in a comment, but it’s being said that AOC slapped this catcaller on the steps of the Capitol and that’s absolutely not true. 

This vid is screen-recorded from her IG stories and it includes the video that the schmuck was recording of himself being disgusting. 

Sorry for the multiple vids, imgur likes to eat the sound on long video uploads unless you chop it up. 

Posted to YT in full: https://youtu.be/ZdRXghO3-tc</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qfFT603.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As always, she makes a great point about the Capitol police and virulent, pervasive sexism. 

I’m sure anyone who has been on the receiving end of sexist harassment can absolutely empathize with the frustration she’s expressing here. I know I can. 

And let’s not forget how she was, very literally, in life-threatening danger on Jan. 6th. And, honestly, still is every single day. I don’t know how she handles it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5DpdlRj.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s fucked that the Capitol police aren’t all fired - I’m sorry - even the innocent ones, even the ones who didn’t help on Jan. 6. If you’re a ‘good cop’ - get a different job because you’re not gonna fix it from the inside. Life isn’t an action movie. ACAB.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CeEM0Vv.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I wish she could have decked him and laid his ass out on the stairs.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l1OolJH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I hope that man gets hit with virulent beer shits, wearing jeans, and stuck in heavy DC traffic on a hot day with a busted AC.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rjPf7yC.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>IG sucks, but her mostly-candid interactions via her stories really gives you a better idea of how incredible she is as a person, as well as a politician. Her tweets are great, but her stories and Lives aren’t scripted or proofread, and she’s still SO eloquent and confident and effective.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qe7KhXX.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Imgur’s good dude to bad dude ratio is getting so much better - it’s one of the reasons I’m here. More often than not, you see sexist and creepy shitheels get knocked down by other people - no matter the gender. 

It makes the internet a slightly less scary place for those of us in marginalized groups.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6C81cON.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GYmbQdZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3fpXlhI.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/B6DGZnj.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v3onwqC.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e1GxUVp.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jbX7HX1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Her most recent statement on the incident.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yrDBSia</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[cuddlesdotgif]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nailed it.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cxFICLu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o7OIkKl.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cxFICLu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dizzyturtle]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Quest Sprout! In order!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tAzS1Q4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bMzq1Ow.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bEXKtSO.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/olMoJVh.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5p0lofw