/imgur.com/a/fItd9xN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tigerliketoightness]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How Fox News works</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UmX9GtR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/To5wh5Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UmX9GtR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[unpopularblargh]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I wonder when they will release the list of the people who went!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JWYUEzw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3n6kivS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JWYUEzw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ice2Ice2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fabulous!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1xYBKPQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Mmj28B1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1xYBKPQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GorgeousGeorgieous]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Blanco Puckett</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vWUQ8TJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rPDSwlp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hi everyone, I'm MrPuckett</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZI43KJN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nashville animal control put out a plea for help last week, being 200% over capacity</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5NLkbbP.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nashville Humane was also over-capacity, WHAT IS HAPPENING</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DTcRF58.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So I asked The Pucketts if they were okay to foster another dog, and after a brief conversation I headed down to Nashville Humane</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qAneMEk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Everyone - meet Blanco!!!!

8 months old and 40lbs he's just a big ole goofy puppy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GDD0U2A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We fell in love on the way home</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/707UCDX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>First thing we did was get him out for adventures

He's so fast and so eager to learn - just a mess on day one and by today he's so good on a leash</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qOldxxF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He and MrsPuckett formed a special bond pretty quick. She can be standoffish at times so this was amazing to see</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ggiazV1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Whenever I leave my place, I always come back to them cuddling</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sW28WnW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>PJ wasn't so sure at first but he's coming around

Blanco doesn't realize he's not a 5lb lapdog.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GUn6kVw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My living situation doesn't allow for a 4th dog, so Blanco will be with us until he gets adopted

Hopefully getting all these pictures will help people see what a lovable adventure dog he really is</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6BfjBhu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Are you near Nashville and looking for a new best friend?

Blanco might be the dude for you!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xgV5AcN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But there is one thing I'll have to warn every potential adopter about --</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/48snY3Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He sneak attacks kisses all the time!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1mncrlc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'll be sad to see him go whenever he gets adopted, but the whole point of this is to find his forever home

If he's been this special to us in only a week, he's going to make someone incredibly happy for many years to come</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pT5hcUu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Look at that face he's such an angel</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AyoDBzS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He taught me that having a 4th dog isn't so tough, and running with 3 dogs is a challenge I'm up for

Maybe when I get in a bigger place I can add another permanent member to the family</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5gxn79L.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He's also learning many things inside the home

Like what the heck to do with bully sticks</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lwRdG9a.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He's just a big puppy who's never had a home but deserves one as much as anyone

While the last week has definitely been a blast, the real treat will be seeing him find his forever home.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IfM4g4c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They just have to make sure to watch out for the kiss attacks. 

We love you MrBlanco, you deserve all the love in the world and you're going to get it.

...

Think you might be a good forever home for Blanco? Check him out here -

https://www.shelterluv.com/embed/animal/NHA-A-18405

...

Have a beautiful day everyone, see you at 1pm central Saturday for TheFreePizzaDude</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vWUQ8TJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MrPuckett]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When the gif is so goddamn adorable you favorite for future use.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/opvrYT8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YRiZyVZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>fun stuff.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/opvrYT8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[deafkitten]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I have no idea why I laughed so hard at this.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/67uIh0I</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tIMorfS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Random vid</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/67uIh0I</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[1324127001]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Priorities straight</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uJPxR19</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SbywGok.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uJPxR19</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JustStonks]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Pretty please!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RiKrsXa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fgyUrWF.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RiKrsXa</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dickblack12]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>At least we know that he wants her :D</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5fYhEGj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o1bTdD2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div># I believe every dog has their own set 